Package: hyperVarMeth
Type: Package
Title: Hypervariable CpG Detection Algorithm (hvCpG)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alice", "Balard", email = "alice.cam.balard@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements batched HDF5-based detection of hypervariable CpG sites 
    across tissues or datasets. Supports parallel processing and automated 
    alpha-parameter optimization per CpG.
